io.sphere.sdk.client

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.client.Log

  • public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
    Internal logging used by the sphere Java client itself. Uses slf4j logger named 'sphere' and does not depend on Play logger (which also uses slf4j loggers, named 'play' and 'application'). The logger can be configured per Play application using 'logger.sphere' in 'application.conf'.
